title: Grading AFC offseason, Cowboys WR concerns (Football 05/21)
description:
Jared Dubin joins Will Brinson to break down the arrest of Terrance Williams and what it might mean for the Cowboys wide receiver depth chart, and then the guys go through each AFC division and break down who had the best and who had the worst offseason from those divisions. There's also some spirited Brad Stevens debate (Brinson thinks he could be the greatest coach in the history of basketball).
